 [gs://google-cloud-aiplatform/schema/dataset/ioformat/text_classification_single_label_io_format_1.0.0.yaml](https://storage.cloud.google.com/google-cloud-aiplatform/schema/dataset/ioformat/text_classification_single_label_io_format_1.0.0.yaml?hl=zh-cn) 
